title: The Best of The Dan Patrick Show
itunes:title: The Best of The Dan Patrick Show
description:
On today's Dan Patrick Show, DP discusses the upcoming documentary from Derek Jeter. Does he expect any news to come out of it? SI's Chris Mannix joins the show and shares which he expects  to be moved out of Brooklyn first, Kyrie or KD. And SI Golf writer Bill Haring discusses what Tiger said at The Open Press Conference today.

See omnystudio.com/listener for privacy information.
